WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:06.000
Draw the Asian range first. High, low, and midline come before direction.

00:06.000 --> 00:13.000
If one candle dominates the box or the high and low keep expanding, the range is messy.

00:13.000 --> 00:20.000
Messy means no trade. The first win is classifying the day correctly.
